data.concurrency-tsdownrolldown#Concurrency (:
Some Rollup-compatible bundlers may execute plugin hooks concurrently (e.g. tsdown/rolldown). To keep evaluation deterministic, @wyw-in-js/rollup serializes transform() calls by default.If you are sure your bundler runs transforms sequentially, you can opt out:
wyw({
  serializeTransform: false,
});

